      <title>进口商称数十年都需要液化天然气来确保能源安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lng-needed-for-decades-to-ensure-energy-security-importers-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个进口商行业组织周一强调，即使世界转向更清洁的能源，未来几十年仍需要液化天然气来确保充足的能源供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lng-needed-for-decades-to-ensure-energy-security-importers-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
